### Get leaderboard (game daily)
GET {{base}}/leaderboard/{{game_id}}?period=daily&scope=game&limit={{limit}}
Accept: application/json

### Get leaderboard (game weekly)
GET {{base}}/leaderboard/{{game_id}}?period=weekly&scope=game&limit={{limit}}
Accept: application/json

### Get leaderboard (global daily)
